HEADWORD: Desmodont
<hw>Des"mo*dont</hw> <pr>(d⟦ecr⟧s"m⟦osl⟧*d⟦ocr⟧nt)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[Gr. <grk>desmo`s</grk> bond + <grk>'odoy`s</grk>,
<grk>'odo`ntos</grk>, tooth.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A member of
